d; --tree-item-expand-collapse-hover: #e5e5e5; --tree-item-expand-collapse-selected-hover: #e0e0e0;"><div class="lm-Widget jp-InputPrompt jp-InputArea-prompt"><button class="jp-Button jp-collapseHeadingButton" data-heading-level="1"></button></div><div class="lm-Widget jp-CodeMirrorEditor jp-Editor jp-InputArea-editor lm-mod-hidden" data-type="inline"><div class="cm-editor ͼ1 ͼ2 ͼ4 ͼo" style=""><div class="cm-announced" aria-live="polite"></div><div tabindex="-1" class="cm-scroller"><div spellcheck="false" autocorrect="off" autocapitalize="off" writingsuggestions="false" translate="no" contenteditable="true" class="cm-content cm-lineWrapping" role="textbox" aria-multiline="true" tabindex="-1" style="tab-size: 4;" data-language="markdown"><div class="cm-line"><span class="ͼr ͼp">#</span><span class="ͼr"> Myntra Fashion Trends Analysis</span></div><div class="cm-line"><br></div><div class="cm-line"><span class="ͼr ͼp">##</span><span class="ͼr"> Objective</span></div><div class="cm-line">To analyze Myntra fashion product data and identify trends related to brands, pricing, and customer ratings.</div><div class="cm-line"><br></div><div class="cm-line"><span class="ͼr ͼp">##</span><span class="ͼr"> Dataset</span></div><div class="cm-line"><span class="ͼp">-</span> Total Products: 14,330</div><div class="cm-line"><span class="ͼp">-</span> Total Features: 11</div><div class="cm-line"><br></div><div class="cm-line"><span class="ͼr ͼp">##</span><span class="ͼr"> Key Findings</span></div><div class="cm-line"><br></div><div class="cm-line"><span class="ͼr ͼp">###</span><span class="ͼr"> Top Brands</span></div><div class="cm-line">Roadster was the most represented brand with 346 products.</div><div class="cm-line"><br></div><div class="cm-line"><span class="ͼr ͼp">###</span><span class="ͼr"> Average Price</span></div><div class="cm-line">The average product price was ₹2964.23.</div><div class="cm-line"><br></div><div class="cm-line"><span class="ͼr ͼp">###</span><span class="ͼr"> Premium Brands</span></div><div class="cm-line">MOKSHA DESIGNS, SAPTRANGI, and Masaba were the most expensive brands.</div><div class="cm-line"><br></div><div class="cm-line"><span class="ͼr ͼp">###</span><span class="ͼr"> Ratings</span></div><div class="cm-line">Most products had ratings between 4.0 and 4.5, indicating generally positive customer satisfaction.</div><div class="cm-line"><br></div><div class="cm-line"><span class="ͼr ͼp">##</span><span class="ͼr"> Conclusion</span></div><div class="cm-line">The analysis revealed that Myntra's marketplace is dominated by a few major brands, while premium brands occupy a smaller but higher-priced segment. Customer ratings are largely positive, suggesting strong overall product satisfaction.</div></div><div class="cm-layer cm-layer-above cm-cursorLayer" aria-hidden="true" style="z-index: 150; animation-duration: 1200ms; animation-name: cm-blink2;"><div class="cm-cursor cm-cursor-primary" style="left: 284.766px; top: 277.812px; height: 15px;"></div></div><div class="cm-layer cm-selectionLayer" aria-hidden="true" style="z-index: -2;"></div></div></div></div><div class="lm-Widget jp-RenderedHTMLCommon jp-RenderedMarkdown jp-MarkdownOutput" data-mime-type="text/markdown"><h1 data-jupyter-id="Myntra-Fashion-Trends-Analysis">Myntra Fashion Trends Analysis<a target="_self" href="http://localhost:8888/lab/tree/Myntra-Analysis#Myntra-Fashion-Trends-Analysis" class="jp-InternalAnchorLink" rel="noopener">¶</a></h1>
<h2 data-jupyter-id="Objective">Objective<a target="_self" href="http://localhost:8888/lab/tree/Myntra-Analysis#Objective" class="jp-InternalAnchorLink" rel="noopener">¶</a></h2>
<p>To analyze Myntra fashion product data and identify trends related to brands, pricing, and customer ratings.</p>
<h2 data-jupyter-id="Dataset">Dataset<a target="_self" href="http://localhost:8888/lab/tree/Myntra-Analysis#Dataset" class="jp-InternalAnchorLink" rel="noopener">¶</a></h2>
<ul>
<li>Total Products: 14,330</li>
<li>Total Features: 11</li>
</ul>
<h2 data-jupyter-id="Key-Findings">Key Findings<a target="_self" href="http://localhost:8888/lab/tree/Myntra-Analysis#Key-Findings" class="jp-InternalAnchorLink" rel="noopener">¶</a></h2>
<h3 data-jupyter-id="Top-Brands">Top Brands<a target="_self" href="http://localhost:8888/lab/tree/Myntra-Analysis#Top-Brands" class="jp-InternalAnchorLink" rel="noopener">¶</a></h3>
<p>Roadster was the most represented brand with 346 products.</p>
<h3 data-jupyter-id="Average-Price">Average Price<a target="_self" href="http://localhost:8888/lab/tree/Myntra-Analysis#Average-Price" class="jp-InternalAnchorLink" rel="noopener">¶</a></h3>
<p>The average product price was ₹2964.23.</p>
<h3 data-jupyter-id="Premium-Brands">Premium Brands<a target="_self" href="http://localhost:8888/lab/tree/Myntra-Analysis#Premium-Brands" class="jp-InternalAnchorLink" rel="noopener">¶</a></h3>
<p>MOKSHA DESIGNS, SAPTRANGI, and Masaba were the most expensive brands.</p>
<h3 data-jupyter-id="Ratings">Ratings<a target="_self" href="http://localhost:8888/lab/tree/Myntra-Analysis#Ratings" class="jp-InternalAnchorLink" rel="noopener">¶</a></h3>
<p>Most products had ratings between 4.0 and 4.5, indicating generally positive customer satisfaction.</p>
<h2 data-jupyter-id="Conclusion">Conclusion<a target="_self" href="http://localhost:8888/lab/tree/Myntra-Analysis#Conclusion" class="jp-InternalAnchorLink" rel="noopener">¶</a></h2>
<p>The analysis revealed that Myntra's marketplace is dominated by a few major brands, while premium brands occupy a smaller but higher-priced segment. Customer ratings are largely positive, suggesting strong overall product satisfaction.</p>
</div></div></div><div class="lm-Widget jp-CellFooter jp-Cell-footer"></div></div><div class="lm-Widget jp-Cell jp-CodeCell jp-Notebook-cell jp-mod-noOutputs jp-mod-active jp-mod-selected" aria-label="Code Cell Content" data-windowed-list-index="21" tabindex="0" style="contain-intrinsic-size: auto 39px; content-visibility: auto; contain: layout style paint;"><div class="lm-Widget jp-CellHeader jp-Cell-header"></div><div class="lm-Widget lm-Panel jp-Cell-inputWrapper"><div class="lm-Widget jp-Collapser jp-InputCollapser jp-Cell-inputCollapser"><div class="jp-Collapser-child"></div></div><div class="lm-Widget jp-InputArea jp-Cell-inputArea" style="--neutral-layer-card-container: #f7f7f7; --neutral-layer-floating: #ffffff; --neutral-layer-1: #ffffff; --neutral-layer-2: #e5e5e5; --neutral-layer-3: #dddddd; --neutral-layer-4: #d5d5d5; --fill-color: #ffffff; --accent-fill-rest: #2675c3; --accent-fill-hover: #176bbf; --accent-fill-active: #3a81c8; --accent-fill-focus: #2675c3; --accent-foreground-rest: #176bbf; --accent-foreground-hover: #135aa0; --accent-foreground-active: #2675c3; --accent-foreground-focus: #176bbf; --neutral-fill-rest: #ededed; --neutral-fill-hover: #e5e5e5; --neutral-fill-active: #f2f2f2; --neutral-fill-focus: #ffffff; --neutral-fill-input-rest: #ffffff; --neutral-fill-input-hover: #ffffff; --neutral-fill-input-active: #ffffff; --neutral-fill-input-focus: #ffffff; --neutral-fill-stealth-rest: #ffffff; --neutral-fill-stealth-hover: #f2f2f2; --neutral-fill-stealth-active: #f7f7f7; --neutral-fill-stealth-focus: #ffffff; --neutral-fill-strong-rest: #757575; --neutral-fill-strong-hover: #616161; --neutral-fill-strong-active: #828282; --neutral-fill-strong-focus: #757575; --neutral-fill-layer-rest: #f7f7f7; --focus-stroke-outer: #878787; --focus-stroke-inner: #fbfdfe; --neutral-foreground-hint: #757575; --neutral-foreground-rest: #2b2b2b; --neutral-stroke-rest: #bebebe; --neutral-stroke-hover: #979797; --neutral-stroke-active: #d5d5d5; --neutral-stroke-focus